#. Id: 19541-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 0.0
#. -- Parent line: -
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: Hire me Ruka
#: 19541-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "Looking at my horns, /FLATSKIN/?"
msgstr ""

#. Id: 19542-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 1.0
#. -- Parent line: 0 (19541-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Target (1)
#. -- Group title: Hire me Ruka
#: 19542-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "Er... no?"
msgstr "呃沒有？"

#. Id: 19545-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 2.0
#. -- Parent line: 1 (19542-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: Hire me Ruka
#: 19545-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "Good. Don't... Because I can still prove my worth in battle without them... I have a question for you, /FLATSKIN/. What do you do if you are outnumbered on the battle field? "
msgstr ""

#. Id: 19548-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 3.0
#. -- Parent line: 2 (19545-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Target (1)
#. -- Group title: Hire me Ruka
#: 19548-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "Fight tactically. You take out the weakest opponents first."
msgstr "戰術上的戰鬥。你先取出最弱的對手。"

#. Id: 19552-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 4.0
#. -- Parent line: 3 (19548-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: Hire me Ruka
#: 19552-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "Truth. We must even the odds against us when our situation looks bleak. We fight the enemy to the death, and we die with honor on the battle field."
msgstr "真相。當我們的情況看起來很黯淡時，我們甚至必須反對我們。我們與敵人戰鬥至死，我們在戰場上以榮譽死亡。"

#. Id: 19553-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 5.0
#. -- Parent line: 4 (19552-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: Hire me Ruka
#: 19553-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "But I didn't die... I awoke, surrounded by death, but still alive. They labeled me a deserter and cut my horns on my return, I'm no longer a warrior... but a servant."
msgstr "但我沒有死...我醒了，被死亡包圍，但還活著。他們給我貼了一個逃兵，並在我回來時砍掉了我的角，我不再是一個戰士......而是一個僕人。"

#. Id: 19554-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 6.0
#. -- Parent line: 5 (19553-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Target (1)
#. -- Group title: Hire me Ruka
#: 19554-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "But you fought bravely. You didn't deserve that."
msgstr "但你勇敢地戰鬥。你不值得這樣。"

#. Id: 19557-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 7.0
#. -- Parent line: 6 (19554-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: Hire me Ruka
#: 19557-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "Perhaps. Either way, I will not remain here as an unclad warrior. But you, you seem different to the other outsiders I have met, /FLATSKIN/... Let us band together, I am intrigued to fight alongside you."
msgstr ""

#. Id: 19558-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 8.0
#. -- Parent line: 7 (19557-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Target (1)
#. -- Group title: Hire me Ruka
#: 19558-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "It would be an honour."
msgstr "這將是一種榮譽。"

#. Id: 19559-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 8.0
#. -- Parent line: 7 (19557-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Target (1)
#. -- Group title: Hire me Ruka
#: 19559-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "Sure, what could go wrong..."
msgstr "當然，可能出現什麼問題......"

#. Id: 19580-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 8.0
#. -- Parent line: 7 (19557-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Target (1)
#. -- Group title: Hire me Ruka
#: 19580-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "I work alone, sorry."
msgstr "我一個人工作，抱歉。"

#. Id: 19582-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 9.0
#. -- Parent line: 8 (19580-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: Hire me Ruka
#: 19582-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "I see. Then see you on the other side, outsider."
msgstr "我知道了。然後在另一邊見到你，局外人。"

#. Id: 19581-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 8.0
#. -- Parent line: 7 (19557-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Target (1)
#. -- Group title: Hire me Ruka
#: 19581-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "I'm not interested..."
msgstr "我沒興趣..."

#. Id: 19555-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 6.0
#. -- Parent line: 5 (19553-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Target (1)
#. -- Group title: Hire me Ruka
#: 19555-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "You lost your horns, but at least you're still alive to fight again."
msgstr "你失去了角，但至少你還活著再次戰鬥。"

#. Id: 19556-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 6.0
#. -- Parent line: 5 (19553-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Target (1)
#. -- Group title: Hire me Ruka
#: 19556-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "You're damn lucky to be alive, horns or no horns."
msgstr "你很幸運能活著，無角或無角。"

#. Id: 19550-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 3.0
#. -- Parent line: 2 (19545-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Target (1)
#. -- Group title: Hire me Ruka
#: 19550-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "You hightail it the hell out of there. Simple."
msgstr "你把它趕出去了。簡單。"

#. Id: 19567-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 4.0
#. -- Parent line: 3 (19550-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: Hire me Ruka
#: 19567-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "So you take the coward's way out. And then... you have to live with that awful shame. Surely that is a worse fate than death?"
msgstr "所以你採取懦夫的方式。然後......你必須忍受那可怕的恥辱。當然這是比死亡更糟糕的命運？"

#. Id: 19568-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 5.0
#. -- Parent line: 4 (19567-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Target (1)
#. -- Group title: Hire me Ruka
#: 19568-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "Not at all. Appreciate your survival, don't dwell on the past."
msgstr "一點也不。欣賞你的生存，不要糾纏於過去。"

#. Id: 19572-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 6.0
#. -- Parent line: 5 (19568-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: Hire me Ruka
#: 19572-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "Interesting. But surviving is for animals, not for warriors. Warriors fight to the death, we die with honour on the battle field."
msgstr "有趣。但倖存的是動物，而不是戰士。勇士們戰死，我們在戰場上以榮譽戰死。"

#. Id: 19569-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 5.0
#. -- Parent line: 4 (19567-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Target (1)
#. -- Group title: Hire me Ruka
#: 19569-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "But at least I'd still be alive."
msgstr "但至少我還活著。"

#. Id: 19570-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 5.0
#. -- Parent line: 4 (19567-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Target (1)
#. -- Group title: Hire me Ruka
#: 19570-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "I suppose you're right. I hadn't thought of it like that."
msgstr "我想你是對的。我沒想過那樣。"

#. Id: 19575-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 6.0
#. -- Parent line: 5 (19570-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: Hire me Ruka
#: 19575-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "It is merely how we are taught in this society. Warriors fight to the death, we die with honour on the battle field."
msgstr "這僅僅是我們在這個社會中被教導的方式。勇士們戰死，我們在戰場上以榮譽戰死。"

#. Id: 19571-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 5.0
#. -- Parent line: 4 (19567-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Target (1)
#. -- Group title: Hire me Ruka
#: 19571-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "Only a fool would choose to die for their own petty honour."
msgstr "只有傻瓜才會選擇為自己的小小榮譽而死。"

#. Id: 19573-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 6.0
#. -- Parent line: 5 (19571-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: Hire me Ruka
#: 19573-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "A warrior is not afraid of laying down their life for honour and comradery. "
msgstr "戰士不怕為了榮譽和同志而犧牲自己的生命。"

#. Id: 19574-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 7.0
#. -- Parent line: 6 (19573-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: Hire me Ruka
#: 19574-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "True humility means sacrifice."
msgstr "真正的謙卑意味著犧牲。"

#. Id: 19547-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 3.0
#. -- Parent line: 2 (19545-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Target (1)
#. -- Group title: Hire me Ruka
#: 19547-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "Is there even a choice? You keep fighting 'til the end."
msgstr "還有選擇嗎？你一直在戰鬥直到最後。"

#. Id: 19561-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 4.0
#. -- Parent line: 3 (19547-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: Hire me Ruka
#: 19561-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "Truth. You live a coward or you die a hero. We fight the enemy to the death, and we die with honor on the battle field."
msgstr "真相。你過著懦夫，或者你死於英雄。我們與敵人戰鬥至死，我們在戰場上以榮譽死亡。"

#. Id: 19549-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 3.0
#. -- Parent line: 2 (19545-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Target (1)
#. -- Group title: Hire me Ruka
#: 19549-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "Surrender and hope your life will be spared."
msgstr "投降，希望你的生命能夠倖免。"

#. Id: 19551-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 3.0
#. -- Parent line: 2 (19545-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Target (1)
#. -- Group title: Hire me Ruka
#: 19551-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "Play dead and return for their heads another day"
msgstr "玩死了，又回到了他們的頭上"

#. Id: 19566-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 4.0
#. -- Parent line: 3 (19551-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: Hire me Ruka
#: 19566-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "Very underhanded, as I might expect from a /FLATSKIN/ I suppose... A Shek warrior, on the other hand, lives to die on the battlefield. "
msgstr ""

#. Id: 19543-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 1.0
#. -- Parent line: 0 (19541-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Target (1)
#. -- Group title: Hire me Ruka
#: 19543-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "I really couldn't care less about your horns."
msgstr "我真的不在乎你的角。"

#. Id: 19562-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 2.0
#. -- Parent line: 1 (19543-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: Hire me Ruka
#: 19562-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "Good... Because I can still prove my worth in battle without them... I have a question for you, /FLATSKIN/. What do you do if you are outnumbered on the battle field? "
msgstr ""

#. Id: 19544-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 1.0
#. -- Parent line: 0 (19541-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Target (1)
#. -- Group title: Hire me Ruka
#: 19544-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "Yeah, I was just thinking how stubby they were."
msgstr "是的，我只是在想他們是多麼粗魯。"

#. Id: 19563-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 2.0
#. -- Parent line: 1 (19544-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: Hire me Ruka
#: 19563-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "Mmh... Well, even so, I can still prove my worth in battle without them... I have a question for you, /FLATSKIN/. What do you do if you are outnumbered on the battle field? "
msgstr ""

#. Id: 19565-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 1.0
#. -- Parent line: 0 (19541-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Target (1)
#. -- Group title: Hire me Ruka
#: 19565-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "No. And I'm leaving."
msgstr "不，我要走了。"
